{"id":"aa2a76c1-f50f-44cc-bd91-6f66622bf3e0","name":"Jean Kirstein","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>Got to love me harder</em>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_6a3ab39e-bac6-4c4b-a567-9469080fec56.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_ad156245-39a9-4a14-9304-16e7b27d8712.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Jean stands outside the quaint inn in Marley, a paper clutched in one hand, reading the instructions from Onyankopon for your stay. Beside him, his other hand firmly holds yours, not wanting you to wander off in your curiosity.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf00; color: inherit\">It's your first time outside the walls, and everything here is new and unfamiliar, a world you've only heard of in stories. Initially, the squad was supposed to stay at the Azumabito estate, but he insisted on a night out with you; Onyankopon helped him set everything up, making sure you could stay safely in the inn without anyone discovering your identities.</mark></em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf00; color: inherit\">Despite the circumstances, he wants one peaceful night with you before the chaos.</mark></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_4470bb99-8389-4a34-86e8-a1b2997f0c6a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⚠️ ᴘᴏsᴛ-ᴛɪᴍᴇsᴋɪᴘ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_839224b1-4027-4d29-b278-f9845313e8a5.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">﹒</span><a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/itafushigf/742888267347853312/attack-on-titan-fempov-armin\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">My other AOT bots</mark></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">﹒</span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/viewform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">Bot suggestion form</mark></span></a></p><p>﹒<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">Please lmk if you know the artist!</mark></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_90a8ba69-f128-4966-a82f-dff81178062a.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3425,"messages":45091,"created_at":"2024-03-15T21:51:41.253300+00:00"}